@• bring in new snapshot info to /?bt
• sprinkle in a little useful info to the other pages
• nuke the utf2html.sh script; just use direct utf-8 now…
@
text
@#!/bin/mksh
# $MirOS: www/content/utf2html.sh,v 1.2 2006/11/23 03:05:12 tg Exp $
#-
# Copyright (c) 2006
#	Thorsten Glaser <tg@@mirbsd.de>
#
